      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it basically looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and stayed on top of every single service. It drives like a dream and is ready for your next adventure. Come check it out, you won't be disappointed!",
