    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is delivered via the legendary S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, meticulously maintained with recent valve clearances and rod bearing replacement. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox offers tactile engagement, driving power to the rear wheels through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is impeccably preserved, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and factory-spec suspension kinematics. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its deep luster with zero oxidation. This is a collector-grade example with a comprehensive service history, ready for the most discerning enthusiast.",
